00 g bean sprouts, to serve","1 - 2 long red chillies, deseeded if preferred and finely sliced, to serve","1 - 2 limes, cut into cheeks, to serve"]}],"id":"r78374","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-aPNVnQCGnIw\/XZMy_PwNDVI\/AAAAAAAAar4\/_Ohn2N0jA5MTQmZeC60knF-tZH6Ab0KyACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_SDUaFS-jBizC0k_b.png","title":"Vietnamese beef pho","publishedAt":"2014-09-06T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"26 g","fat":"10 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"17 g","calories":"1181 kJ \/ 281 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ceramic or glass bowl, large bowl, large jug, 6 serving bowls, colander","hintsAndTricks":["If you cannot buy beef bones pre-cut into pieces please ask your butcher to cut your beef bones into pieces for you. We do not recommend you do this yourself at home."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 45m","6 portions"]}